query:
SELECT 
  id,
  gestanteId,
  tipoUltrassom,
  dataExame,
  idadeGestacional,
  JSON_PRETTY(dados) as dados_formatado,
  createdAt,
  updatedAt
FROM ultrassons 
WHERE gestanteId = (SELECT id FROM gestantes WHERE email = 'dreatnu@yahoo.com')
ORDER BY dataExame;
